source.name: Maryland Total New Parcels Inside PFA For Residential Development: 2006-2009
source.description:
Maryland Total New Parcels inside Priority Funding Areas (PFA) for residential development from 2006 to 2009. 
Priority Funding Areas are existing communities and places where local governments want State investment to support furture growth.
